&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: South Africa - long-term contract&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedules available: &lt;/strong&gt;1pm to 10pm EST – Monday to Friday. Sunday to Wednesday: 6pm to 5am EST.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary: &lt;/strong&gt;R35,000 – R50,000 ZAR / month&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
